---
// V3-B: Mobile = Antes full-width + 2 Depois lado a lado | Desktop = 3 colunas
---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 bg-transparent overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-emerald-500 mb-8">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="font-medium">Nota Máxima no Google Pagespeed</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6 leading-tight font-['Outfit']">
        O Site Que Transforma Seus Anúncios em <span class="text-[#6366F1]">Clientes no WhatsApp</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
        Nossa infraestrutura garante que nenhuma oportunidade seja perdida. Substituímos seu site lento por uma estrutura focada em uma única coisa: fazer seu telefone tocar.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center lg:justify-start justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl py-3 px-5 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        <span class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400 whitespace-nowrap">5 em 10</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-zinc-300 text-center sm:text-left">clientes perdidos por sites lentos <span class="text-zinc-500">(Google)</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="#planos" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base px-8 py-4 bg-[#6366F1] text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(99,102,241,0.4)] transition-all">
          Ver Planos
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M7 1l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Direita: Opção B -->
    <div class="relative w-full mt-8 lg:mt-0 space-y-4">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-indigo-500/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

      <!-- ── MOBILE ── -->
      <div class="lg:hidden space-y-3 relative z-10">
        <div class="flex justify-between text-xs font-mono px-1">
          <span class="text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Antes</span>
          <span class="text-[#6366F1] uppercase tracking-widest">Depois — escolha o objetivo</span>
        </div>
        <!-- Antes: full width, proporção 9:16 -->
        <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-zinc-800">
            <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/60"></div><div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/40"></div><div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="aspect-[9/16] flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-zinc-700 border-t-red-400 rounded-full animate-spin"></div>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 text-center leading-relaxed">A página está carregando...<br/>O cliente já desistiu.</p>
            <div class="text-sm text-red-400 font-mono bg-red-500/10 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">4.5 segundos ▼</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 2 Depois: lado a lado -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 border border-[#6366F1]/30 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900 px-2 py-2 flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-zinc-800">
              <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/60"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 min-h-[180px]">
              <div class="w-full space-y-1.5"><div class="h-1.5 bg-zinc-700 rounded-full w-3/4 mx-auto"></div><div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full w-1/2 mx-auto"></div></div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-emerald-500 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/></svg>
                WhatsApp
              </div>
              <div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-mono">0.8s ✓</div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[9px] text-zinc-500 text-center pb-2">Contato & Serviços</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 border border-[#6366F1]/30 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900 px-2 py-2 flex items-center gap-1 border-b border-zinc-800">
              <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/60"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 min-h-[180px]">
              <div class="w-full space-y-1.5"><div class="h-1.5 bg-zinc-700 rounded-full w-3/4 mx-auto"></div><div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full w-1/2 mx-auto"></div></div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#6366F1] text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 01-8 0"/></svg>
                Comprar
              </div>
              <div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-mono">0.8s ✓</div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[9px] text-zinc-500 text-center pb-2">Vendas & E-commerce</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── DESKTOP: 3 colunas ── -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block space-y-3 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Antes</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-mono text-[#6366F1] uppercase tracking-widest col-span-2">Depois — escolha o objetivo</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
          <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900 px-2 py-2 flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-zinc-800"><div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/60"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/40"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div></div></div>
            <div class="p-4 h-56 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 border-2 border-zinc-700 border-t-red-400 rounded-full animate-spin"></div>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-zinc-600 text-center leading-tight">Carregando...<br/>aguarde</p>
              <div class="text-[10px] text-red-400 font-mono bg-red-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">4.5s ▼</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 border border-[#6366F1]/30 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900 px-2 py-2 flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-zinc-800"><div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/60"></div></div></div>
            <div class="p-4 h-56 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-full space-y-2"><div class="h-1.5 bg-zinc-700 rounded-full w-3/4 mx-auto"></div><div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full w-1/2 mx-auto"></div></div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-emerald-500 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/></svg>
                WhatsApp
              </div>
              <div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-mono bg-emerald-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">0.8s ✓</div>
              <p class="text-[9px] text-zinc-500">Contato & Serviços</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 border border-[#6366F1]/30 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900 px-2 py-2 flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-zinc-800"><div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/60"></div></div></div>
            <div class="p-4 h-56 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-full space-y-2"><div class="h-1.5 bg-zinc-700 rounded-full w-3/4 mx-auto"></div><div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full w-1/2 mx-auto"></div></div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#6366F1] text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 01-8 0"/></svg>
                Comprar Agora
              </div>
              <div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-mono bg-emerald-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">0.8s ✓</div>
              <p class="text-[9px] text-zinc-500">Vendas & E-commerce</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[#111115]/60 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-2xl py-4 px-5 text-center relative z-10">
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">Seja para <span class="text-white font-medium">gerar contato</span> ou <span class="text-white font-medium">vender diretamente</span> — entregamos a página certa para cada objetivo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
